  "texts": [
    "Fig. 1 Design process of an iVR experience with biosensors",
    "• Standalone: the device works as a stand-alone console where different applications are uploaded or downloaded.",
    "No computer is needed, although sometimes it can be connected with a cable to become a Desktop.",
    "• Cardboard: a holder mount that is connected to a mobile phone.",
    "It tracks head rotation, but not user movement in space."
  ]
